
  Syntax:	cast 'chainlightning'
  Damage:	1d30 for every level up to level 25
    Type:	Electricity
    Area:	Yes
   Touch:	No
    Cost:	100 Mana
MinSpeed:	Short
    Save:	vs. electricity for half damage

This spell will unleash a powerfull lightning bolt that will arc from foe to
foe, electrocuting as many as it can. However, the bolt becomes weaker as it
rips through each foe, reducing damage down by a dice per foe. Once the spell
decreases to 0d30, it will disappate.

